paragraphs.text:
Without expressing any opinion on the merits of the case and considering the nature of accusation and having no criminal antecedents, applicant is directed to cooperate in the investigation as also the interim protection granted by this Court vide order dated 14.08.2024 is made absolute in view of dictum of Apex Court in re: 
Sushila Aggarwal Vs. State (NCT of Delhi
)-2020 SCC online SC 98.
